rComments: Jim Dalling is very dedicated to his field and his excitement shows through in his lectures. Although it is sometimes hard to keep focused during lecture if you participate every once in a while he will know you care about biology and about his course.
I think he's a super nice guy. Really chill and always willing to work with students
He is very helpful and I learned a lot in this class! Lectures are really interesting and well organized. You can tell he knows his stuff, and generally wants to help, if you ask for it.
This guy is the best of the three professors of IB 101, hands down. He speaks with clarity and fluency despite his accent. I found him to be an awesome professor.
